{
  "stem": "4700.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's like the Asians today in Australia, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jealous of their progress, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I should think-- I should think so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I should think so, because everybody worked as much-- you weren't forced to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You worked because you wanted to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think, [SIGHS] thinking back, I thought she must have had some-- my mother was very well-read.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she used to read magazines-- English magazines and German papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She used to go to-- one used to go to a coffee shop and read.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was extremely well-informed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think she could see what was happening in Germany--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think she probably took our money out of the bank.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because-- I can't remember, well, we were never flush.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I can't remember that we would have been completely penniless--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--like some people were when the accounts were frozen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was afraid that then I would be pushed aside, or that maybe-- I don't know, what was-- also, she didn't have the opportunity.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--she only saw fathers and mothers, sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she-- Well, they were all married people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were the parents of my friends and the parents of her pupils and--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, she-- she was wonderful, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She never spared any money to give me some special education.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to lessons-- gymnastic lesson and dance lessons and music lessons and this and that, English and whatever I wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I wanted to learn the graphic arts, so I was going there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to go on holidays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to take-- seeing that she wasn't working all the school holidays--",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
